description:
Value: {252.1*} 
Includes the series of clause numbers to be ignored. * indicates the series - 252.1* means it would ignore all the clauses starting with 252.1 

NOTE: * is important here to specify it as a series. If not specified this would be checked for exact match. Eg. 252.1 would match only the clause number "252.1" and 252.1* would match "252.100-7000" and "252.122-7001" etc..
